Hildesheim&ndash;Z&uuml;rich&ndash;New York: Georg Olms Verlag,
35&ndash;61.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2021, <em>A New Survey of Plutarch</em>,
Cambridge: Cambridge University Press,</li>

<li>Roskam, G. and L. Van der Stockt (eds.), 2011, <em>Virtues for the
People: Aspects of Plutarchean Ethics</em>, Leuven: Leuven University
Press.</li>

<li>Russell, D.A., 1973, <em>Plutarch</em>, London: Duckworth.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1989, &ldquo;Plutarch,&rdquo; in G. Kennedy
(ed.), <em>The Cambridge History of Literary Criticism</em> (Volume
1), Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 302&ndash;306.</li>

<li>Santaniello, C., 1999, &ldquo;Traces of the lost Aristotle in
Plutarch,&rdquo; in <em>Plutarco, Platon y Arist&ocirc;teles</em>:
<em>Actas del V Congresso Internacional de la IPS</em>, Madrid:
Ediciones cl&aacute;sicas, 628&ndash;641.</li>

<li>Schoppe, Ch., 1994, <em>Plutarchs Interpretation der Ideenlehre
Platons</em>, M&uuml;nster: Lit.</li>

<li>Schrenk, L. P., 1991, &ldquo;A Middle Platonic Reading of
Plato&rsquo;s Theory of Recollection,&rdquo; in <em>Ancient
Philosophy</em>, 11: 103&ndash;110.</li>

<li>Schr&ouml;der, St., 1990, <em>Plutarch Shrift De Pythiae
Oraculis</em>, Stuttgart: Beitr&auml;ge zur Altertumskunde 8.</li>

<li>Shiffman, M., 2010, &ldquo;Erotic Wisdom and the Socratic Vocation
in Plutarch&rsquo;s <em>Platonic Question</em> 1&rdquo;, <em>Greek
Roman and Byzantine Studies</em>, 50: 243&ndash;271.</li>

<li>Sierksma-Agteres, S., 2015, &#8190;Say Goodbye to Opinions!&rsquo;
Plutarch&rsquo;s Philosophy of Natural Phenomena and the Journey to
Metaphysical Knowledge, in M. Meeusen, and L. Van Der Stockt (eds.),
<em>Aspects of Plutarch&rsquo;s Philosophy of Nature</em>, Leuven:
Leuven University Press, 57&ndash;71.</li>

<li>Stadter, P. A., 2005, &ldquo;Plutarch and Apollo of Delphi,&rdquo;
in R. Hirsch&ndash;Luipold (ed.), <em>Gott und die G&ouml;tter bei
Plutarch. G&ouml;tterbilder&ndash;Weltbilder</em>, Berlin&ndash;New
York: De Gruyter.</li>

<li>Teodorsson, S.-T., 1994, &ldquo;The psychology of <em>De
facie</em> and <em>De virtue morali</em>,&rdquo; in M. G.
Vald&eacute;s (ed.), <em>Studios sobre Plutarco: ideas religiosas.
Actas del III Simposio Internacional sobre Plutarco</em>, Madrid:
Ediciones Cl&aacute;sicas, 115&ndash;122.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1999, &ldquo;Plutarch and Peripatetic
Science,&rdquo; in <em>Plutarco, Platon y Arist&ocirc;teles. Actas del
V Congresso Internacional de la IPS</em>, Madrid: Ediciones
Cl&aacute;sicas, 665&ndash;674.</li>

<li>Titchener, F. B., and A. V. Zadorojnyi (eds.), 2023, <em>The
Cambridge Companion to Plutarch</em>, Cambridge: Cambridge University
Press.</li>

<li>Th&eacute;venaz, P., 1938, <em>L&rsquo;&Acirc;me du monde, le
devenir et la mati&egrave;re chez Plutarque</em>, Neuch&acirc;tel: Les
Belles Lettres.</li>

<li>Ulacco, A., 2017, <em>Pseudopythagorica Dorica. I trattati di
argomento metafisico, logico ed epistemologico attribuiti ad Archita e
a Brotino. Introduzione, traduzione, commento</em>, Berlin: De
Gruyter.</li>

<li>Valgiglio, E., 1973, <em>Plutarco De audiendis poetis</em>,
Torino: Loescher.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1989, &ldquo;La teologia di
Plutarco,&rdquo; in <em>Prometheus</em>, 14: 253&ndash;265.</li>

<li>Van der Stockt, L., 1990, &ldquo;L&rsquo;experi&eacute;nce
esth&eacute;tique de la mimesis selon Plutarque,&rdquo; in
<em>Quaderni urbinati di cultura classica</em>, 65: 23&ndash;31.</li>

<li>Van Hoof, L., 2010, <em>Plutarch&rsquo;s Practical Ethics</em>,
Oxford: Oxford University Press 2010.</li>

<li>Warren, J., 2011, &ldquo;Pleasure, Plutarch&rsquo;s <em>Non
Posse</em> and Plato&rsquo;s <em>Republic</em>, &rdquo; <em>Classical
Quarterly</em>, 61: 278&ndash;293.</li>

<li>Weiss, R. 1977, <em>Medieval and Humanist Greek: Collected
Essays</em>, Padua: Editrice Antenore.</li>

<li>Westman, R., 1955, <em>Plutarch gegen Kolotes</em>, <em>Acta
Philosophica Fennica</em>, 7, Helsinki.</li>

<li>Whittaker, J. 1969, &ldquo;Ammonius on the Delphic E&rdquo;,
<em>Classical Quarterly</em>, 63, 185&ndash;192.</li>

